Status:
Submitted for review the hierarchical configuration support. Along with some headless tests.

<@U1KFBBWG1> - I checked out your PR - looks pretty good.  I believe that it is failing CI because CI is using  down-level of NodeJS.    See <https://jira.hyperledger.org/browse/FAB-725>  where I suggest that we mark this fact in package.json

<@U12J2D15H> this morning I discovered that you can convert a task in JIRA to subtask of a story. i think it’d be a good idea to convert FAB-133 to 138 to subtasks to 132, so you don’t have to continue to move them in bundles in the board
